{"tid":1156909,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"歸根究底，所有人都係自私？","createTime":"2019-05-16T02:00:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-16T16:18:22.000Z","uid":76143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"5aa3b96602eeda8bab0e3384f3940b07d51d536b","tid":1156909,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:00:45.000Z","msg":"我相信世界上所有人<br />\n都係經過第一身去思考<br />\n用自己產生嘅諗法<br />\n去做行動或者判斷<br />\n咁係咪引伸出 <br />\n人嘅所有行為其實都係自私嘅行為呢<br />\n<br />\n例如<br />\n有一個人堅決犧牲自己換取其他人生存<br />\n但係佢會令到身邊嘅人傷心<br />\n咁可唔可以話呢個人係自私<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ffcde9d2a10e60ef494a9d7a691ff8376cb6839","tid":1156909,"uid":46488,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:09:54.000Z","msg":"Not the general definition of selfishness.<br />\nSelfishness, in economics term, is to consider only yourself in your utility function."},{"pid":"1f0c4151d31aab1438fdc83fb7a68a14ef116da6","tid":1156909,"uid":2404,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T02:15:01.000Z","msg":"有一個人入餐廳食飯，最後佢食完飯埋單畀錢<br />\n<br />\n呢個人入餐廳係咪為咗畀錢？"},{"pid":"00f0657800baa4b668563754dd9f4ea496583a79","tid":1156909,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:51:07.000Z","msg":"人唔自私都唔會生存到今日，所以自私只係本能。"},{"pid":"07f870511e7351794ac7ece271a448c00d75db8c","tid":1156909,"uid":17569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T15:51:57.000Z","msg":"所以咪行資本主義"},{"pid":"eeb77e10fff84dcb02a3c1221a5989ea01cdf73c","tid":1156909,"uid":76143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-16T16:18:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}